com.tsgrp.migration.event.pipeline

Class PipelineSummaryWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tsgrp.migration.event.AbstractListener
      • com.tsgrp.migration.event.pipeline.PipelineSummaryWriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PipelineEndDisengageEventListener, PipelineEndEngageEventListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PipelineSummaryWriterBatch

    public class PipelineSummaryWriter
extends AbstractListener
implements PipelineEndEngageEventListener, PipelineEndDisengageEventListener
    Pipeline Summary Writer writes out entire properties file summarizing the state of the pipeline. Called when pipeline is done engaging, after each target thread iteration is complete, and at end of disengage.
